# Deployment

After pushing changes to GitHub, deploy to the Linode server:

```bash
sshpass -p 'HMsmile543!mh' ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no hcinst_user@173.255.232.249 \
  "cd /home/hcinst_user/hci-website && git pull && npm run build && pm2 restart hci-website"
```

- Server: 173.255.232.249 (Linode Nanode, Ubuntu 24.04)
- User: `hcinst_user`
- App dir: `/home/hcinst_user/hci-website`
- Process manager: PM2 (process name: `hci-website`)
- Reverse proxy: Nginx (serves `/uploads/` directly from filesystem)
- Database: SQLite at `/home/hcinst_user/hci-website/prisma/prod.db`

Always deploy after committing and pushing code changes. Wait for the build to complete and verify PM2 shows "online" status.
